====Interjection====
{{head|bg|interjection|tr=a|sc=Cyrl}}

# {{non-gloss definition|used to express surprise or wonder}}: {{l|en|ah}}, {{l|en|oh}}, {{l|en|ha}}, {{l|en|why}}
#: {{ux|bg|'''А''', ето къде си бил!|Ah, there you are!|inline=1}}
#: {{ux|bg|'''А''', значи ти хареса.|Oh, so you liked it.|inline=1}}
#: {{ux|bg|'''А'''! Не те видях.|Oh! I didn't see you there.|inline=1}}
#: {{ux|bg|'''А''', Джейн, ти ли си!|Why Jane, it's you!|inline=1}}
# {{non-gloss definition|used to express pleasure, relief}}: {{l|en|ah}}
#: {{ux|bg|'''А''', пролетните цветя.|Ah, the flowers of spring.|inline=1}}
#: {{ux|bg|'''А''', спомням си старите времена.|Ah, I remember the good old days.|inline=1}}
# {{non-gloss definition|used when you are not certain about something and you would like confirmation}}: {{l|en|eh}}, {{l|en|well}}, {{l|en|right}}, or translated with a {{l|en|tag question}}
#: {{ux|bg|Хареса ти, '''а'''?|So, you liked it, eh/did you?|inline=1}}
#: {{ux|bg|Утре заминаваш, '''а'''?|You're leaving tomorrow, right?|inline=1}}
# {{label|bg|colloquial}} {{non-gloss definition|used to indicate that one did not hear what was said}}: {{l|en|eh}}, {{l|en|huh}}
#: {{ux|bg|‘Не съм гладен.’ ‘'''А'''?’ ‘Казах, че не съм гладен.’|‘I'm not hungry.’ ‘Eh?’ ‘I said I'm not hungry.’|inline=1}}
#: {{ux|bg|'''А'''? Какво каза?|Huh? What did you say?|inline=1}}
# {{non-gloss definition|used to express understanding, recognition, or realization}}: {{l|en|oh}}
#: {{ux|bg|'''А''', значи така работело.|Oh, so that's how it works.|inline=1}}
#: {{ux|bg|'''А''', сега ми дойде на ум!|Oh, I’ve just thought of it.|inline=1}}
#: {{ux|bg|'''А''', да, сетих се!|Oh, yes, I remember.|inline=1}}
# {{non-gloss definition|used to express displeasure, objection}}
#: {{ux|bg|Изпуснал влака … ама работа, '''а'''!|So he missed the train … what a damned nuisance!|inline=1}}
#: {{ux|bg|'''А''', той ще ми каже!|He's not the one to tell me!|inline=1}}
#: {{ux|bg|Ще ми се плезиш, '''а'''!|Don't stick out your tongue at me!|inline=1}}
# {{non-gloss definition|used to express criticism or disapproval}}: {{l|en|now}}
#: {{ux|bg|'''А'''-'''а''', така не може!|Now, this sort of thing can’t go on/won’t do!|inline=1}}
